text: Aurel Loşniţă (born 2 November 1927) was a Romanian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
